(80, 'T20201903250033', 'Suresh', 'AMAZING KASHMIR', '2025-04-25', '2025-04-29', 3, 1, '<ul><li>04 Nights In Hotel&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>MAPAI basis ( Breakfast + Dinner)</li><li>All sightseeing &amp; transfers by &nbsp; NON&nbsp;AC Suv</li><li>01 hour shikara ride&nbsp; -4 paxs using 01 boat</li><li>Toll, tax, driver allowance for all trips</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Gondola To be booking online only&nbsp;( Kindly book it online from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.jammukashmircablecar.com/\">https://www.jammukashmircablecar.com/</a></li><li>Tickets to all gardens &amp; monuments&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;Arru Betaab Valley &amp; Chanwari in Pahalgam&nbsp;</li><li>Thajiwas Glacier / Zero point in Sonmarg</li><li>Snow&nbsp;Jeep&nbsp;transfers from Tangmarg to Gulmarg to Tangmarg&nbsp;: If there is heavy snow</li><li>Snow Jeep in Sonmarg From Gagangir : If there is heavy snow</li><li>All optional items&nbsp;</li></ul>', '<p><strong>OPTION&nbsp;1&nbsp;:3 STAR HOTEL</strong></p><p><strong>78500 INR COST FOR (3 ADUTLS +1 KID)</strong></p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>City</td><td>Hotel</td><td>Check-in</td><td>Check-out</td><td>Nights</td><td>Room Title</td></tr><tr><td>Srinagar&nbsp;</td><td>Adlife luxury&nbsp;</td><td>25/04/2025</td><td>29/04/2025</td><td>4</td><td>Family room&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><strong>OPTION&nbsp;1&nbsp;:4 STAR HOTEL</strong></p><p><strong>92500 INR COST FOR (3 ADUTLS +1 KID)</strong></p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>City</td><td>Hotel</td><td>Check-in</td><td>Check-out</td><td>Nights</td><td>Room Title</td></tr><tr><td>Srinagar&nbsp;</td><td>Arison luxury&nbsp;</td><td>25/04/2025</td><td>29/04/2025</td><td>4</td><td>&nbsp;Suite room&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/travels2020/image/upload/v1742390950/Travels2020/lequlkq43nfhd7zsbmxn.jpg', '<p><strong>Important&nbsp;Notes :</strong></p><p>&nbsp;1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No Cars are allowed to move inside 